---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
const APP_URL = 'https://app.erdify.com';
---

<DocsLayout title="Developer Center — ERDify" activePage="overview">
  <div class="dc-hero">
    <div class="dc-badge">Developer Center</div>
    <h1>ERDify와 연결하기</h1>
    <p>AI 도구에 MCP로 연결하거나, REST API로 직접 통합하세요.<br />두 방법 모두 API 키 하나로 시작할 수 있습니다.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="dc-cards">
    <a href="/docs/mcp-integration" class="dc-card">
      <div class="dc-card-icon">🤖</div>
      <div class="dc-card-body">
        <h2>MCP 연동</h2>
        <p>Cursor, Claude Desktop, Gemini CLI, Codex CLI에서 자연어로 ERD를 읽고 수정합니다.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>설정 파일 한 줄로 연결</li>
          <li>스키마 조회·수정·관계 설정</li>
          <li>DDL·ORM 코드 바로 생성</li>
        </ul>
        <span class="dc-card-link">MCP 가이드 보기 →</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/docs/api-reference" class="dc-card">
      <div class="dc-card-icon">⚡</div>
      <div class="dc-card-body">
        <h2>REST API</h2>
        <p>HTTP 요청으로 스키마를 조회·수정하고 DDL을 내보냅니다. CI/CD·스크립트·서드파티 통합에 적합합니다.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Bearer 토큰 인증</li>
          <li>JavaScript · Python SDK 지원</li>
          <li>DDL 내보내기 (MySQL·PostgreSQL·MariaDB)</li>
        </ul>
        <span class="dc-card-link">API 레퍼런스 보기 →</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="dc-quickstart">
    <h2>빠른 시작</h2>
    <ol class="dc-steps">
      <li>
        <span class="dc-step-num">1</span>
        <div>
          <strong>API 키 발급</strong>
          <p>ERDify 앱 → <strong>설정 → API</strong> 에서 API 키를 발급받으세요.</p>
          <a href={`${APP_URL}/settings/api`} class="dc-inline-link">키 발급하기 →</a>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="dc-step-num">2</span>
        <div>
          <strong>연동 방법 선택</strong>
          <p>AI 도구를 사용하면 <a href="/docs/mcp-integration" class="dc-inline-link">MCP 연동</a>, 직접 통합이 필요하면 <a href="/docs/api-reference" class="dc-inline-link">REST API</a>를 선택하세요.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="dc-step-num">3</span>
        <div>
          <strong>연결 확인</strong>
          <p>MCP라면 AI 도구에서 "현재 ERD 테이블 목록 보여줘"를 입력해 보세요. API라면 <code>/v1/projects</code>를 호출해 프로젝트 목록을 확인하세요.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  .dc-hero {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .dc-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--primary);
    background: #EEF4FF;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .dc-hero h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .dc-hero p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-sub);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .dc-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .dc-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 28px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--white);
    transition: border-color 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s;
  }
  .dc-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,100,224,0.08);
  }
  .dc-card-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .dc-card-body h2 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .dc-card-body p { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .dc-card-body ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .dc-card-body ul li { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-sub); padding-left: 16px; position: relative; }
  .dc-card-body ul li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; }
  .dc-card-link { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); margin-top: auto; }

  .dc-quickstart h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .dc-steps { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .dc-steps li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .dc-steps li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .dc-step-num {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .dc-steps strong { display: block; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .dc-steps p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.65; }
  .dc-steps code {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .dc-inline-link { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; }
  .dc-inline-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .dc-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .dc-hero h1 { font-size: 28px; }
  }
</style>
